      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "私達の目標はあくまで長瀬麻奈です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our goal one and only goal is Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 5.883560276031494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "え……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.883560276031494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 7.15761923193932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "この三年間、長瀬麻奈より自分達が上であることを\n証明するために、私達は頑張ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During the past three years‚ we wanted to show everyone that we’re better than Mana Nagase.\nThat’s what we’ve worked so hard for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.957619231939317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そのためにも、この大会では負ける訳にはいかない\n必ず優勝します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And to that end‚ we cannot let ourselves be defeated in this competition.\nWe will win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.55761923193932,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7500.000000000007,
          "startTime": 22.490952565272657
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.524285898605985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 24.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 26.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 26.8
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 27.033333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、緊張した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohh‚ I was so nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.833333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、最後にメンバー全員\n一言求められるなんてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought they’d ask all of us at the end\nfor a comment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 35.43333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "もう、心臓止まるかと思った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought my heart would stop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ちゃんと言えたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you were able to talk‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 41.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……{user}さん。少しだけ\n別行動してもいいですか？　練習までには戻ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… {user}? Can I be on my own\nfor a bit? I’ll be back in time for rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。別にいいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. I don’t mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 51.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.666666666673,
          "startTime": 54.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 55.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします\n琴乃ちゃんのこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please look after\nKotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 59.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 59.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "多分、莉央さんに会いに行ったんだと思います\n……気にしていたみたいだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think she went to talk to Rio.\nShe seemed preoccupied with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私より、きっと{user}さんが\nいてくれた方がいいと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think instead of me‚ you would be\na good person to be there for her‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 70.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは大丈夫ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll all be okay without you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった\n行ってくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.\nI’ll go check on her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 75.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 75.7
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 75.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈が、どんなアイドルだったか……って\nそれを私に聞く？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of idol was Mana Nagase?\nIs that what you wanted to ask me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 83.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "はい。変ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Is that weird?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私、当時はアイドルのお姉ちゃんのこと\nあまり知ろうとしてなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s just‚ at the time‚ I never really attempted\nto get to know her as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにアイドルを始めたの？\n麻奈が亡くなってから？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yet you still became an idol?\nAfter your sister died?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 96.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 98.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……そう。お姉さんのために？\nアイドルに興味ないのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You did this for your sister?\nEven though you had no interest in being an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 103.36666666666666
    },
    {
